<br>
Monks have 2nd best melee damage in the game, it's not appropriate for them to be best tanks as well.<br>
<br>
MONKS TANK BETTER THEN WARRIORS RIGHT NOW. The only thing warriors have going for them are:<br>
Shit load of hps<br>
Defensive/Evasive<br>
<br>
That's just not right. If monks are moved to just below warriors in tanking ability (meaning how much damage they take) it would be cool, or even a bit lower below plate melees in general. It sucks that they do this now, and we will have to rework our strats, but that's how it goes.<br>
<br>
<br>
There are some glaring errors in EQ. I am glad that they are willing to make hard decisions to fix them. I just hope they find some good stuff to give mages. Unless pets become viable on raids, mages still get the short end of the stick (End game, they rock in XP groups). <p><html>
